üèÜ Recent Developments

In 2024, CUBE expanded its capabilities by acquiring U.S.-based regulatory businesses, including Reg-Room and Thomson Reuters Regulatory Intelligence and Oden products. This strategic move enhanced their content infrastructure and broadened their regulatory coverage. Ôøº

